                                    <div class="faq-section" style="margin-top: 40px;">
                                        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                                        <h3>How much does it cost to build a multi-vendor marketplace app in India in 2026?</h3>
                                        <p>Indicative ranges: MVP (single city, single vertical) &#8377;6.5L–&#8377;10L over 4–6 weeks; Growth (multi-city, full vendor + rider apps + dashboard) &#8377;15L–&#8377;25L over 3–4 months; Enterprise (multi-country, AI dispatch, mission-critical) &#8377;35L+ over 6+ months. ITD GrowthLabs publishes fixed-scope quotes after a 30-minute discovery call.</p>
                                        <h3>What is included in a multi-vendor marketplace MVP?</h3>
                                        <p>A typical MVP at ITD GrowthLabs includes a customer app on Android + iOS, a lite web vendor panel, a basic admin dashboard, one payment gateway, onboarding for up to 50 vendors, and 30 days of post-launch support. It's enough to prove demand and unit economics in one city before scaling.</p>
                                        <h3>How long does it take to build a marketplace app like Swiggy or Blinkit?</h3>
                                        <p>A Swiggy-style multi-restaurant marketplace MVP can launch in 4–6 weeks using ITD GrowthLabs' reusable modules. A full feature-parity build (with hyperlocal radius, surge pricing, vendor onboarding, rider dispatch, advanced analytics) takes 12–14 weeks. Enterprise-grade clones with multi-city dark-store routing take 5–6 months.</p>
                                        <h3>Should I use a white-label SaaS or build a custom marketplace app?</h3>
                                        <p>White-label (Yelo, Growcer, FATbit) makes sense if you need to launch in under two weeks and accept platform-imposed limits. Custom is the right choice once you need unique workflows (cold chain, prescription gating, B2B credit), 100% source-code ownership, or a funding-grade tech moat. Most funded marketplaces transition from white-label to custom within 9–12 months.</p>
                                        <h3>Will I own the source code and the apps?</h3>
                                        <p>Yes — with ITD GrowthLabs' default custom-build engagement you receive 100% source-code ownership, the database, deployment scripts, and admin credentials. Apps are published under your own Apple and Google developer accounts. There is no vendor lock-in.</p>
                                        <h3>What ongoing costs should I budget for after launch?</h3>
                                        <p>Plan for cloud hosting (&#8377;25k–&#8377;1.5L/month at growth scale), Google Maps / Mapbox API usage (&#8377;30k–&#8377;1L/month), SMS + WhatsApp messaging (&#8377;0.15–&#8377;0.50 per message), Apple developer fee ($99/year), and a maintenance retainer (&#8377;40k–&#8377;1.5L/month depending on feature velocity).</p>
